  "title": "Galaxy in Flames",
  "synopsis": "The Warmaster returns from Davin a different man, and the Legions he can trust go where he sends them. On the dead-grey world of Isstvan III, four Legions — Sons of Horus, World Eaters, Emperor's Children, Death Guard — deploy in force against a recalcitrant planetary governor. What they cannot know is that the deployment is the trap. From orbit their own brothers burn loyalist elements to ash with life-eater virus and atomic fire; in the ruins, Garviel Loken, Tarik Torgaddon, Saul Tarvitz and Nathaniel Garro hold cathedral and bunker as the bombardment turns the world into a graveyard. The Horus Heresy is no longer a rumour. Let the galaxy burn.",
